WEBVTT

00:02.415 --> 00:05.355
It's a magical storybook
which we're all written into.

00:05.463 --> 00:07.985
This book, could change
Regina's future for the better.

00:08.010 --> 00:10.380
Ingrid.
She locked me in here.

00:10.385 --> 00:11.680
We're going to sneak you
out of here,

00:11.686 --> 00:14.158
and then steal back the urn
and then trap her inside it.

00:14.325 --> 00:15.513
I can help you.

00:16.024 --> 00:16.825
Henry!

00:16.843 --> 00:19.077
<i>My magic is hurting people, Gold.
People I love.</i>

00:19.202 --> 00:20.507
I need you
to help me control it.

00:20.513 --> 00:21.808
You meet me here at sundown.

00:21.856 --> 00:23.223
I'll have averything prepared.

00:23.589 --> 00:25.044
Remember the urn?

00:25.069 --> 00:26.979
<i>It had the power
to limit your magic.</i>

00:27.004 --> 00:28.489
<i>The dust won't last long.</i>

00:28.495 --> 00:32.531
<i>When I escape,
there will be a terrible price to pay.</i>

